I"â<h1 id="openproject-avatars">OpenProject Avatars</h1>

<p>To select which type of Avatars can be used in your OpenProject, navigate to -&gt; <em>Administration</em> -&gt; <em>Users &amp; Permissions</em> -&gt; <em>Avatars</em>.</p>

<p>You can choose whether to allow user Gravatar or enable to upload custom avatars.</p>

<p>The Avatars can be configured via the <a href="../users">user profile</a>.</p>

